      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 12,
      "quran_arabic": "قَالُوا۟ تِلْكَ إِذًۭا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٌۭ",
      "text": "They will say, ‘That would then be a losing turn!’",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 13,
      "quran_arabic": "فَإِنَّمَا هِىَ زَجْرَةٌۭ وَٰحِدَةٌۭ",
      "text": "Yet it will only be a single shout,",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 14,
      "quran_arabic": "فَإِذَا هُم بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ",
      "text": "and suddenly they will be awakened.",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 15,
      "quran_arabic": "هَلْ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ مُوسَىٰٓ",
      "text": "Has the story of Moses come to you?",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 16,
      "quran_arabic": "إِذْ نَادَىٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ بِٱلْوَادِ ٱلْمُقَدَّسِ طُوًى",
      "text": "When his Lord called to him in the holy wādī of Ṭuwā:",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 17,
      "quran_arabic": "ٱذْهَبْ إِلَىٰ فِرْعَوْنَ إِنَّهُۥ طَغَىٰ",
      "text": "‘Go to Pharaoh! Surely he has transgressed insolently.",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 18,
      "quran_arabic": "فَقُلْ هَل لَّكَ إِلَىٰٓ أَن تَزَكَّىٰ",
      "text": "And say: “Do you have (any desire) to purify yourself?”",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 19,
      "quran_arabic": "وَأَهْدِيَكَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَتَخْشَىٰ",
      "text": "And: “I would guide you to your Lord, and then perhaps you will fear (Him).”’",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 20,
      "quran_arabic": "فَأَرَىٰهُ ٱلْءَايَةَ ٱلْكُبْرَىٰ",
      "text": "So he showed him the great sign,",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 21,
      "quran_arabic": "فَكَذَّبَ وَعَصَىٰ",
      "text": "but he called (it) a lie and disobeyed.",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 22,
      "quran_arabic": "ثُمَّ أَدْبَرَ يَسْعَىٰ",
      "text": "Then he turned away in haste,",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 23,
      "quran_arabic": "فَحَشَرَ فَنَادَىٰ",
      "text": "and he gathered (his people) and called out,",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 24,
      "quran_arabic": "فَقَالَ أَنَا۠ رَبُّكُمُ ٱلْأَعْلَىٰ",
      "text": "and said, ‘I am your Lord, the Most High!’",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 25,
      "quran_arabic": "فَأَخَذَهُ ٱللَّهُ نَكَالَ ٱلْءَاخِرَةِ وَٱلْأُولَىٰٓ",
      "text": "So God seized him with the punishment of the last and the first.",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 26,
      "quran_arabic": "إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَعِبْرَةًۭ لِّمَن يَخْشَىٰٓ",
      "text": "Surely in that is a lesson indeed for whoever fears.",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 27,
      "quran_arabic": "ءَأَنتُمْ أَشَدُّ خَلْقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ ۚ بَنَىٰهَا",
      "text": "Are you a stronger creation or the sky? He built it.",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
