      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 40,
      "quran_arabic": "وَأَمَّا مَنْ خَافَ مَقَامَ رَبِّهِۦ وَنَهَى ٱلنَّفْسَ عَنِ ٱلْهَوَىٰ",
      "text": "But as for the one who feared the position of his Lord, and restrained himself from (vain) desire,",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
