    {
      "verse": 41,
      "quran_arabic": "فَإِنَّ ٱلْجَنَّةَ هِىَ ٱلْمَأْوَىٰ",
      "text": "surely the Garden – it will be the refuge.",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
    },
    {
      "verse": 42,
      "quran_arabic": "يَسْـَٔلُونَكَ عَنِ ٱلسَّاعَةِ أَيَّانَ مُرْسَىٰهَا",
      "text": "They ask you about the Hour: ‘When is its arrival?’",
      "canonical_variants": [],
      "competing_variants": []
